  "programma": "<table><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">1) La Sicurezza di un sistema gerarchico</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 1.a\u00a0 \u00a0Gli obiettivi del security layer: autenticazione delle parti, confidenzialit\u00e0 e integrit\u00e0, non ripudiabilit\u00e0</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 1.b\u00a0 \u00a0Crittografia simmetrica e asimmetrica</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 1.c\u00a0 \u00a0PKI, certificati digitali</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 1.d\u00a0 \u00a0La firma elettronica</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 1.e\u00a0 \u00a0Il protocollo SSL/TLS\u00a0\u00a0</span></span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">2) La Sicurezza di un sistema cooperativo</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 2.a\u00a0 \u00a0Formalizzazione di un sistema cooperativo attraverso WFL</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 2.b\u00a0 \u00a0Monitoraggio dei task e delle applicazioni</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 2.c\u00a0 \u00a0Anomaly detection systems e analisi delle reti</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 2.d\u00a0 \u00a0Entropia e monitoraggio dei processi\u00a0</span></span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">3) La Sicurezza di una rete sociale</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 3.1\u00a0 \u00a0Definizione di social network e social network analysis\u00a0</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 3.2\u00a0 \u00a0Analisi locale e globale di una social network</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 3.3\u00a0 \u00a0La funzione di trust</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 3.4\u00a0 \u00a0Costruzione di un firewall applicativo attraverso la SNA\u00a0</span></span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">4) La Sicurezza di un sistema distribuito</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a04.1\u00a0 Sistemi non gerarchizzabili e approcci distribuiti ai problemi</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a04.2\u00a0 \u00a0Distributed Ledgers Technology e Blockchain theory</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a04.3\u00a0 \u00a0Sicurezza nelle DLT</span></span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p></td></tr></table>",
